TITLE: Webhook Signature Verification in PHP
DESCRIPTION: PHP implementation for verifying Mailgun webhook signatures with timestamp validation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/user_manual.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function verify($signingKey, $token, $timestamp, $signature)
{
    // check if the timestamp is fresh
    if (\abs(\time() - $timestamp) > 15) {
        return false;
    }

    // returns true if signature is valid
    return \hash_equals(\hash_hmac('sha256', $timestamp . $token, $signingKey), $signature);
}
```

