TITLE: Webhook Signature Verification in Go
DESCRIPTION: Go implementation for verifying Mailgun webhook signatures using the mailgun-go library.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/user_manual.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
import (
    "github.com/mailgun/mailgun-go/v3"
)

func VerifyWebhookSignature(domain, signingKey, timestamp, token, signature string) (bool, error) {
    mg := mailgun.NewMailgun(domain, signingKey)

    return mg.VerifyWebhookSignature(mailgun.Signature{
        TimeStamp: timestamp,
        Token:     token,
        Signature: signature,
    })
}
```

