TITLE: Webhook Signature Verification in Ruby
DESCRIPTION: Ruby implementation for verifying Mailgun webhook signatures using OpenSSL HMAC-SHA256.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/user_manual.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: ruby
CODE:
```
require 'openssl'

def verify(signing_key, token, timestamp, signature)
  digest = OpenSSL::Digest::SHA256.new
  data = [timestamp, token].join
  signature == OpenSSL::HMAC.hexdigest(digest, signing_key, data)
end
```

