TITLE: Sending Complex Messages with Attachments using Go
DESCRIPTION: This Go function uses the mailgun-go library to send a complex email with attachments. It creates a new message with sender, subject, text body, and recipient, then adds CC and BCC recipients, sets HTML content, attaches JPG and TXT files, and sends the message with a timeout context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/samples/send-complex-message.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: go
