TITLE: Retrieving IP Information using Go Mailgun SDK
DESCRIPTION: This Go function uses the Mailgun Go SDK to retrieve information about a specific IP address. It initializes the Mailgun client with the domain and API key, then calls the GetIP method with a context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/samples/get-ip.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
import (
    "context"
    "github.com/mailgun/mailgun-go/v3"
    "time"
)

func GetIP(domain, apiKey string) (mailgun.IPAddress, error) {
    mg := mailgun.NewMailgun(domain, apiKey)

    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), time.Second*30)
    defer cancel()

    return mg.GetIP(ctx, "127.0.0.1")
}
```

