SOURCE: https://github.com/mailgun/documentation.git/blob/master/source/api-deliverability-alerts.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: ruby
CODE:
```
require "json"
require "openssl"

def verify(signing_key, webhook_payload, signature)
  data = JSON.generate(webhook_payload)

  signature == OpenSSL::HMAC.hexdigest("SHA256", signing_key, data)
end
```

